You make it sound like tradition is nothing.  If it were not for Tradition you would not have a Bible to begin with.  The Church existed for 400 years without an agreed upon canon of the New Testament.  The foundational doctrinal statement the Nicene Creed was published before the New Testament Canon was firmed up. <br>
